<paragraph id="F3A30278DE057DA28F3F4B4B08E76A93" pageId="3" pageNumber="138">China (Tibet, Shaanxi, Sichuan, Zhejiang, Taiwan), Korea, Japan, Russia, India, Myanmar, Afghanistan.</paragraph>
